---
title: Notification Module - User Flow Diagram V2
description: Updated user flow matching Figma screenshots (Notification panel, Live Activity, task completion updates)
date: 07-03-26
version: V2
---

flowchart TD
    Start([User Logs In]) --> Dashboard[Dashboard View]
    
    %% Notification Bell Icon
    Dashboard --> NotificationBell[Notification Bell Icon]
    NotificationBell --> CheckBadge{Check Unread Badge}
    
    %% No Notifications State
    CheckBadge -->|0 Unread| NoNotifications[No Notifications<br/>"There's no notifications"<br/>Empty state illustration]
    
    %% Has Notifications
    CheckBadge -->|Has Unread| HasNotifications[Notification Panel]
    HasNotifications --> ShowNotifications[Show Notifications List<br/>Alax tom - Complete math homework<br/>5 min ago]
    
    ShowNotifications --> NotificationItem{Notification Item}
    NotificationItem -->|Click| ViewDetails[View Notification Details<br/>Task completion details]
    NotificationItem -->|Swipe| MarkAsRead[Mark as Read]
    
    ViewDetails --> HasTaskLink{Has Task Link?}
    HasTaskLink -->|Yes| NavigateToTask[Navigate to Task<br/>View task details]
    HasTaskLink -->|No| ShowContent[Show Content Only]
    
    NavigateToTask --> MarkAsRead
    ShowContent --> MarkAsRead
    
    MarkAsRead --> MoreNotifications{More Notifications?}
    MoreNotifications -->|Yes| ShowNotifications
    MoreNotifications -->|No| ViewAllButton[View All Notifications Button]
    
    ViewAllButton --> AllNotificationsPage[All Notifications Page]
    AllNotificationsPage --> FilterNotifications{Filter Notifications}
    
    FilterNotifications -->|By Type| FilterByType[Filter by Type<br/>Task, Group, System, Reminder]
    FilterNotifications -->|By Date| FilterByDate[Filter by Date<br/>Today, Yesterday, Older]
    FilterNotifications -->|By Status| FilterByStatus[Filter by Status<br/>Read, Unread]
    
    FilterByType --> ShowFilteredList[Show Filtered List]
    FilterByDate --> ShowFilteredList
    FilterByStatus --> ShowFilteredList
    
    ShowFilteredList --> BulkActions{Bulk Actions}
    BulkActions -->|Mark All Read| MarkAllRead[Mark All as Read]
    BulkActions -->|Delete Old| DeleteOld[Delete Old Notifications]
    BulkActions -->|Clear All| ClearAll[Clear All Notifications]
    
    MarkAllRead --> Done[Done ✅]
    DeleteOld --> Done
    ClearAll --> Done
    
    %% Live Activity Feed (From Figma Dashboard)
    Dashboard --> LiveActivity[Live Activity Section<br/>Real-time updates from family]
    LiveActivity --> ShowLiveUpdates[Show Live Updates<br/>"Jamie Chen completed Complete math homework<br/>2 minutes ago"]
    
    ShowLiveUpdates --> LiveUpdateAction{Live Update Action}
    LiveUpdateAction -->|Click| ViewTaskDetails[View Task Details]
    LiveUpdateAction -->|Dismiss| DismissUpdate[Dismiss Update]
    
    ViewTaskDetails --> TaskCompleted[Task Completed View<br/>Sub-tasks progress<br/>Member completion status]
    
    %% Task Completion Notification Flow
    Dashboard --> TaskCompletion[Task Completion Event]
    TaskCompletion --> MemberCompletes[Member Completes Task<br/>e.g., "Jamie Chen completes task"]
    MemberCompletes --> TriggerNotification[Trigger Notification]
    
    TriggerNotification --> CreateNotification[Create Notification Record<br/>Type: task<br/>Priority: normal<br/>Channel: in_app]
    CreateNotification --> SendToRecipients[Send to Recipients<br/>Primary user<br/>Other members]
    
    SendToRecipients --> UpdateBadge[Update Notification Badge<br/>Increment unread count]
    UpdateBadge --> ShowInPanel[Show in Notification Panel]
    ShowInPanel --> AddToLiveActivity[Add to Live Activity Feed]
    
    %% Notification Settings (From Figma Profile)
    Dashboard --> ProfileNav[Profile Navigation]
    ProfileNav --> ProfilePage[Profile Page]
    ProfilePage --> NotificationStyle[Notification Style Settings]
    
    NotificationStyle --> SelectStyle{Select Notification Style}
    SelectStyle -->|Gentle| GentleStyle[Gentle Style<br/>Soft and non-intrusive]
    SelectStyle -->|Firm| FirmStyle[Firm Style<br/>Direct and clear]
    SelectStyle -->|XYZ| XYZStyle[XYZ Style<br/>Custom style]
    
    GentleStyle --> SaveStyle[Save Preference]
    FirmStyle --> SaveStyle
    XYZStyle --> SaveStyle
    
    SaveStyle --> StyleSaved[Style Saved ✅]
    
    %% Support Mode Integration (Affects Notification Tone)
    ProfilePage --> SupportMode[Support Mode Settings]
    SupportMode --> SelectMode{Select Support Mode}
    SelectMode -->|Calm| CalmMode[Calm Mode<br/>Gentle guidance with peaceful reminders]
    SelectMode -->|Encouraging| EncouragingMode[Encouraging Mode<br/>Positive energy with motivational reminders]
    SelectMode -->|Logical| LogicalMode[Logical Mode<br/>Gentle guidance with peaceful reminders]
    
    CalmMode --> SaveMode[Save Mode]
    EncouragingMode --> SaveMode
    LogicalMode --> SaveMode
    
    SaveMode --> ModeSaved[Mode Saved ✅<br/>Affects notification tone]
    
    %% Styling
    style Start fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style Done fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style StyleSaved fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style ModeSaved fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style NoNotifications fill:#FF9800,color:#fff
    style HasNotifications fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
    style LiveActivity fill:#E91E63,color:#fff
